{"tid":2423943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"下周起進入法院大樓需使用「安心出行」或填寫登記表格 籲勿手寫以節省時間","createTime":"2021-02-26T08:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:42:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5eada79fd0f823be614ce2df5c6b74dc6478ddc","tid":2423943,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"下周起進入法院大樓需使用「安心出行」或填寫登記表格<br />\n<br />\n下周一起，所有進入法院大樓的人士必須使用「安心出行」流動應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構表示，沒有使用程式掃瞄二維碼的人士，必須將其姓名、聯絡電話、到訪法院大樓的日期和時間記錄在登記表格。<br />\n<br />\n所有不使用程式並拒絕記錄聯絡資料的人士，將不獲准進入法院大樓。法庭使用者進入法院大樓時難免會花較多時間，期望市民預先下載並嘗試使用程式，並提早到達法院，尤其於早上或午飯後的繁忙時段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577693-20210226.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577693-20210226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd60pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=73af4463\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577693-20210226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1af51ce3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577693-20210226.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"28fffce72c06496ed8518a7c1d687f8ba8d6c84c","tid":2423943,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:31:27.000Z","msg":"唔柒用咪唔使嘥時間囉戇鳩"},{"pid":"3ac4dff71e84c341d93d6a60fef440d570be12dc","tid":2423943,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"手寫同嘟卡有冇相差一分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f28f0eeb0f51c765a3359763024460d40c6aec2","tid":2423943,"uid":353256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ac4dff71e84c341d93d6a60fef440d570be12dc","tid":2423943,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"